{"tid":1451143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咪撚成日focus勇武派","createTime":"2019-08-11T18:24:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T18:40:41.000Z","uid":152746,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"535a98de68ecb27208e2ce853953333ac62ac240","tid":1451143,"uid":152746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:24:44.000Z","msg":"有無人講下和理非？<br />\n<br />\n和理非係大多數人<br />\n幾時先肯出手<br />\n幾時先肯覺醒<br />\n個個係到屌li屌路 又唔肯出多分力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗住出黎集會行個圈打下卡就算？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">嬲有用咩？</span> 嬲完麻煩做實事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">家陣唔使你衝<br />\n但麻煩各自搵有意義既野去做 <br />\n文宣又好 乜都得 憑良心<br />\n最簡單聽日<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">機場見</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n推到所有和理非見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">但係個人都認同勇武係要抖一抖 重整下先既</span>"},{"pid":"a729e9a1710f0cb5d14b26e69e90695f0c3724f0","tid":1451143,"uid":152746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:25:03.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"dfba31a120abd4b3fb97dbf83bc11594e9598335","tid":1451143,"uid":152746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:25:34.000Z","msg":"係香港最黑暗既日子"},{"pid":"750abb799086e3a3f2dcc295b126813eb017ea64","tid":1451143,"uid":34063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:25:53.000Z","msg":"有小小指責成份,我相信係樓主太嬲打錯字咋<br />\n兄弟爬山,各地開花<br />\n<br />\n邊個話我哋輸緊嘅我屌晒你哋老母！要嬴嘅全部同我入嚟！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dBbvRS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dBbvRS</a><br />\n<br />\n推,所有掟磚同火魔法都係黑警扮示威者做既<br />\n緊記要事：<br />\n1. 尖沙咀瞄頭射，射爆女仕眼球<br />\n2. 721無起訴<br />\n3. 狗扮示威者<br />\n4. 室內射tear gas<br />\n5.一米同胡椒球對人發射<br />\n6.罔顧安全,推人落電梯<br />\n7.黑警插贓嫁禍,塞管狀物體入示威者背囊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/POs3Lz7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=htt